      • Switch

        public static final int[] Switch
        Attributes that can be used with a Switch.

        Includes the following attributes:

        AttributeDescription
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:switchMinWidth Minimum width for the switch component
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:switchPadding Minimum space between the switch and caption text
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:switchTextAppearance TextAppearance style for text displayed on the switch thumb.
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:textOff Text to use when the switch is in the unchecked/"off" state.
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:textOn Text to use when the switch is in the checked/"on" state.
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:thumb Drawable to use as the "thumb" that switches back and forth.
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:thumbTextPadding Amount of padding on either side of text within the switch thumb.
        jforce.com.caterpillarcount:track Drawable to use as the "track" that the switch thumb slides within.
        See Also:
        Switch_switchMinWidth, Switch_switchPadding, Switch_switchTextAppearance, Switch_textOff, Switch_textOn, Switch_thumb, Switch_thumbTextPadding, Switch_track
